TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.STAGESALESTRANSACTIONSEQ as STAGESALESTRANSACTIONSEQ, CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.ORDERID as ORDERID, CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.PRODUCTNAME as PRODUCTNAME, TO_CHAR(CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.COMPENSATIONDATE ,'YYYYMM') as TXN_DATE FROM CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ORDERID = O_ORDER_ID AND PRODUCTNAME = TXT_LEVEL_CD AND TXN_DATE = O_TXN_DATE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(DTE_TXN_DATE) ,'DTE_TXN_DATE is null. ','')||IIF(ISNULL(TXT_CMP_CD) OR TXT_CMP_CD='','TXT_CMP_CD is null . TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: ERROR_MSG

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_ST_OPMSRATE.DEC_RECORD_NO, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.DTE_TXN_DATE, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.TXT_CMP_CD, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.TXT_LEVEL_CD, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.TXT_AGENCY_CODE, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.DEC_ASSIGN_RAGE, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.DEC_DISCONTINUANCE, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.DEC_CVF_RATE, IN_ST_OPMSRATE.DEC_XSELL_RATE, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_VALUE FROM IN_ST_OPMSRATE, IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING='OPMS_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.DEC_RUNNING_FLG =1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.NAME AS BU_NAME, B.NAME AS POS_NAME, B.GENERICATTRIBUTE2 AS GA2 FROM CS_BUSINESSUNIT A, CS_POSITION B, CS_PAYEE C WHERE A.MASK = C.BUSINESSUNITMAP AND A.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ = B.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ AND B.PAYEESEQ = C.PAYEESEQ

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE IN_ETL_CONTROL SET TXT_KEY_VALUE=(SELECT LPAD(TO_CHAR(COUNT(*)),10,'0') FROM IN_ST_OPMSRATE WHERE TXT_ERROR_MSG IS NOT NULL ), DTE_UPDATE_DATE=SYSDATE WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='OPMS_STAGE_RECORD_COUNT' and DEC_RUNNING_FLG='1';
COMMIT;
